messages.text: I spy with my little eye…
You look so beautiful in that dress..
how do u kno what dress im wearing?!
yes it does!! ur freaking me out..
I saw you. Tried to show these messages to your friends..
I’m not going to hurt you, unless you give me away.
and y r u messaging me?!
and how’d u get this number?!
So many questions, but I just wanna talk with you.
If you don’t, all your friends in there might not make it to tomorrow..
That tone is not helping you.
wat do u want from me?!
but i dont have ur number saved..
I know. For stupid reasons I had to get a new one.
We spent summers down at Lake Corrigen.
I held you when mom and dad were fighting.
When dad hit mom that one time.
im not the one who can do that 4 u..
I know you havent given up on family..
I know what I did was wrong..
wrong!?!? it was perverted and sick and disgusting!!
I just was overcome by emotion.
not after wat u did 2 me..
Then you leave me no choice..
ur lucky im not callin the cops!!
u beling n a mental asylum
The say goodbye to your friends..
He was hanging all over you all night.
I will if you do what I say…
Do you want that pretty girl n the pink dress to go next?
I said walk to the right.
Hurry. The cops will certainly be here now.
wat do u want from me??
I can’t do this without you.
Go without my baby sis, my family…
Then say goodbye to everyone in there…
We’re gonna have a lot of fun together...
